               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17440912-47-off240-c294" targOrder="Y" targets="t17440912-47-defend374 t17440912-47-off240 t17440912-47-verdict242"></join>
         
               <p>401. 
               
                  <persName id="t17440912-47-defend374" type="defendantName">
                     Rebecca 
                     Smith 
                  <interp inst="t17440912-47-defend374" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-defend374" type="given" value="Rebecca"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-defend374" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17440912-47-off240" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-off240" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-off240" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing four pewter plates, value 1 s. two pewter dishes, value 1 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17440912-47-victim376" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Appleton 
                  <interp inst="t17440912-47-victim376" type="surname" value="Appleton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-victim376" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-victim376" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17440912-47-off240 t17440912-47-victim376"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17440912-47-cd241" type="crimeDate">July 6</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17440912-47-off240 t17440912-47-cd241"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17440912-47-person377">
                  John 
                  Appleton 
               <interp inst="t17440912-47-person377" type="surname" value="Appleton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-person377" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-person377" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The Prisoner came to borrow some water, she went down into the cellar for it: I missed the pewter after she was gone, and charged her with taking it, for nobody had been in the cellar but herself; she denied the taking it, but I found it by her direction.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17440912-47-person378">
                  Edward 
                  Drinker 
               <interp inst="t17440912-47-person378" type="surname" value="Drinker"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-person378" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-person378" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The Prisoner brought two pewter plates of Mr. Appleton's to me to pawn, I asked her whether they were her own? She said, they were: said I, they may not be your's, though you have the use of them, you may be in a ready furnished lodging, she said, By G - d they are mine. <rs id="t17440912-47-verdict242" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-verdict242" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-verdict242" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17440912-47-punish243" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-punish243" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17440912-47-punish243" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17440912-47-defend374 t17440912-47-punish243"></join>
               
                     <note>[Whipping. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
